1.4 Data Storage
================

All data lives in a single SQLite database at ‘GNOSIS-DIR/gnosis.db’.
The database is created and migrated automatically; no manual setup or
maintenance is required.  Gnosis requires Emacs 29.1 or later (for
built-in SQLite support) and the ‘compat’ library.  There are no other
external dependencies.


